galing sa Cinemalaya at sa iba pang mga festival na kagaya nito.', 'Ang Galing ng Pelikulang Pinoy: Cinemalaya Films Go International', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-15 20:29:52', '2018-03-16 00:29:52', '', 16, 'http://throughtheeyes.info/iteration1/2018/03/15/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
