vie with its heart in the right place.\r\n\r\nAnd making it was a truly delightful Cinemalaya experience.', 'Acting for Cinemalaya Made Me Realize...', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '66-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-16 01:07:57', '2018-03-16 05:07:57', '', 66, 'http://throughtheeyes.info/iteration1/2018/03/16/66-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
